                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <section>
        <div class="container py-5">
            <div class="row">
                <!-- Text Section -->
                <div class="col-md-12">
                    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4" style="font-size: 55px;">The Next Level in Support and Protection</h2>
            </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="row">
                        <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; ">Advanced Threat Detection</p>
                        <p>Offers an extra layer of defense against complex threats like phishing scams, malware, and ransomware that basic settings might not catch.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; ">AI-Powered Email Filtering</p>
                        <p>Utilize intelligent technology to identify and block deceptive emails before they reach your inbox with smart detection.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; ">Employee Security Awareness Training</p>
                        <p>Empower your team with interactive training to help them recognize and avoid email scams, reducing the risk of human error.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="row">
                        <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; ">Simulated Phishing Exercises</p>
                        <p>Real-world practice with regular, safe simulations to improve your team’s ability to spot and report suspicious emails.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; ">Data Loss Prevention</p>
                        <p>Protect confidential data and prevent accidental or unauthorized sharing of sensitive information via email.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; ">Detailed Reporting and Insights</p>
                        <p>Understand your security posture with comprehensive reports on threats blocked and training progress to help you make informed decisions.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-5 bg-gradient-x" style="background: linear-gradient(180deg, #F3F3F4 48.5%, #EAFBFF 100%);">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center">
                <!-- Left Section -->
                <div class="col-md-5">
                    <h2 class="fw-bold mb-4" style="font-size: 64px; line-height: 79px;">Learn About Protection You Can Count On</h2>
                    <p class="mb-3 py-2" style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 22px;">
                        Reach out today to see how we can help your organization get to the next level, by implementing world class cybersecurity - without the overhead.
                    </p>
                    <h4 class="fw-bold mt-4" style="font-size: 24px;">Still want more information?</h4>
                    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 22px;">
                        Prospector FAQs are also a great place to learn more. You can also view service offerings
                        tailored to fit your needs and learn more about how Prospector can serve you.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Right Section: Form -->
                <div class="col-md-7">
                    <form id="contactForm" class="p-4 shadow rounded bg-white">
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="name" class="form-label">Name</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="email" class="form-label">Email</label>
                            <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="phone" class="form-label">Phone</label>
                            <input type="tel" class="form-control" id="phone" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label for="company" class="form-label">Company</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="company">
                        </div>
                        <div class="py-3">
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-hero btn-lg">Submit
                                <svg
                                  xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                                  width="22"
                                  height="22"
                                  fill="currentColor"
                                  class="bi bi-arrow-right-circle align-middle ms-2"
                                  viewBox="0 0 16 16"
                                >
                                    <path
                                      fill-rule="evenodd"
                                      d="M1 8a7 7 0 1 0 14 0A7 7 0 0 0 1 8m15 0A8 8 0 1 1 0 8a8 8 0 0 1 16 0M4.5 7.5a.5.5 0 0 0 0 1h5.793l-2.147 2.146a.5.5 0 0 0 .708.708l3-3a.5.5 0 0 0 0-.708l-3-3a.5.5 0 1 0-.708.708L10.293 7.5z"
                                    />
                                </svg>
                            </button>
                        </div>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script>
        document.getElementById('contactForm').addEventListener('submit', function(event) {
            event.preventDefault();

            const formData = {
                name: document.getElementById('name').value,
                email: document.getElementById('email').value,
                phone: document.getElementById('phone').value,
                company: document.getElementById('company').value
            };

            fetch('https://formspree.io/f/xwpvbgnv', {
                method: 'POST',
                headers: {
                    'Content-Type': 'application/json'
                },
                body: JSON.stringify(formData)
            })
              .then(response => response.json())
              .then(data => {
                  console.log('Success:', data);
              })
              .catch((error) => {
                  console.error('Error:', error);
              });
        });
    </script>

</Layout>
